newarticletext: Owu ora igọọk ugọbọ inu lek akọp ìkakup-nu. Ire òbobene akpọk yi, bene kige inu tap me emen okop eyi irak yi (kpọ [$1 akpọk ntap-ubọk] ire oweek ofifi etip igbaalek). Ire ke ònu me okariọọn̄ge, keme ubọk me lek ichip back me òwọlọ-olik kwun̄.
anontalkpagetext: ---- Eyi ìre akpọk ukpatu òkup inyi ogwu òsikwaan̄ ogwu ìkasan̄a erieen̄ kan̄ ìsibi, ogwu ìkachili-nu irek ikwaan̄, mè ìre ìkakisa irọ ikwaan̄. Eya orọ eji esabe ifuk eyi IP address isa ijeen̄ ema. Owuwa ene mêkọt ikaan̄ ojelek IP address yaage. Ire owu ire òsikwaan̄ ogwu ìkasan̄a erieen̄ kan̄ isibi, mè ikeek ibe ke mîtumu owuwa ikọ ikagbege ikikpọ ere owu okupbe, soso [[Special:CreateAccount|chili irek ikwaan̄]] mè ìre [[Special:UserLogin|tibi nin̄]] inyi wọlọwọlọ ikakup òborọ es owu egwen ufi ene.
